      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for stopping by to check out my pride and joy! This car is honestly a total dream\u2014it's been babied since the day I got it and looks just as gorgeous as it did on the showroom floor. It\u2019s been kept tucked away in a garage, so the paint is flawless and the interior is still smelling fresh. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and I know the next owner is going to absolutely love it. I'm looking for a smooth sale, so I've priced it to be a steal for whoever grabs it first! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
