    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S is an exemplary specimen of the 996.2 generation, featuring the iconic wide-body silhouette and high-performance chassis derived from the Turbo. At its heart is a 3.6L naturally aspirated flat-six engine equipped with VarioCam Plus and integrated dry-sump lubrication, delivering seamless power through a tactile six-speed manual transaxle. The sophisticated all-wheel-drive system ensures optimal torque distribution, complemented by factory-spec monoblock four-piston calipers and ventilated rotors for superior thermal management. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, with meticulous attention to suspension geometry and drivetrain integrity. A mechanically pristine, collector-grade example for the discerning enthusiast.",
